verbose_text: When we analyzed PRR mediated cytokine expression, we found that TLR2 mediated expression of IL-6 mRNA, TLR4 mediated expression of IL-6 and IL-10 mRNA, TLR5 mediated expression of IL-6, IL-10, and TNF-alpha mRNA, TLR9 mediated expression of IL-6 mRNA, and NOD2 mediated expression of IL-6, IL-12, and TNF-alpha mRNA were significantly lower in obese than in non obese children.
